sparse.eigenvolvers.java
Class Utilities

java.lang.Object
  sparse.eigenvolvers.java.Utilities

public class Utilities
extends java.lang.Object

SEIG Java Utilities class.

SEIG uses the MTJ Java library (matrix-toolkits-java) and Netlib Java (netlib-java) for numerical linear algebra and matrix computations.

The Utilities class consists of a set of useful methods for running and testing eigenvalue problems and doing numerical linear algebra

Author:
Rico Argentati
